ensures the beans soften fully before sugar is added in the final cooking stage.<br>- Azuki beans (also called adzuki or aduki beans), white rice flour and glutinous rice flour are available in Asian or Japanese supermarkets.<br>- You can make azuki bean paste in advance and chill for up to <nobr>1 week,<\/nobr> or purchase it ready-made."],"basicInfo":["medium","35m","8h 30m","6 portions"]}